description: Feed the family with tasty honey soy chicken skewers, and save time with a ready-made crunchy broccoli slaw.
name: Quick Chicken Skewers Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 375 g bottle Masterfoods honey soy garlic marinade

recipeInstructions.text: In a bowl, toss the broccoli slaw together with the dressing and cranberries from the kit, then divide among plates and top with skewers. Drizzle over garlic sauce to serve.
